Musio: So, what do you think about altruism?

User: Well, I think it's a good thing. It's when you help other people without expecting anything in return.

Musio: Why do you think people should help others without expecting anything in return?

User: I guess because it's the right thing to do. And it makes the world a better place.

Musio: Do you think everyone is capable of being altruistic?

User: I don't know. I guess some people might not be able to help others as much as others can. But I think everyone has the potential to be altruistic in some way.

Musio: What do you think motivates people to be altruistic?

User: I guess they just care about others and want to make a difference.